[It is interesting that so far in Utah there have been only 2 deaths (case fatality rate under 1 percent) whereas the large outbreaks in southern California and southeastern Michigan reported case fatality rates of 3-4 percent. The hospitalization rate in Utah while high is also substantially below the 70-80 percent rate in those other outbreaks.

